headline: Agoda Launches AI-Powered Bot to Instantly Answer Hotel Questions
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has officially launched the Property AMA ("Ask Me Anything") Bot, an AI chatbot designed to provide instant answers to travelers' hotel-specific questions. This innovation aims to help users make quicker, more confident booking decisions by cutting through the clutter and delivering precise information in seconds.
